frus:attachment.p:
The President of the German Reich, the President of the French Republic, His
                        Majesty the King of Great Britain, Ireland and the British Dominions beyond
                        the Seas, Emperor of India, and His Majesty the King of Italy;

Convinced that the state of disquiet which obtains throughout the world can
                        only be dissipated by reinforcing their solidarity in such a way as to
                        strengthen confidence in peace in Europe;
